like":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfdf887685349029643cb746754335b67af044df","tid":795476,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T06:00:27.000Z","msg":"咁你又叫人黑鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T07:52:53.000Z","msg":"即使阿姆哈拉人同阿拉伯人、猶太人都係「閃米特民族」，另類白鬼（高加索人種）<br />\n<br />\n阿姆哈拉人已經同非洲各種黑鬼融合咗，所以叫佢哋黑鬼多過白鬼，雖然非洲嘅閃米特人（唔計古埃及人）本來都係膚色較黑，但當然啦，人種呢家嘢用膚色嚟計都已經不合時宜，最起碼都應該用顱骨結構、基因、遺傳學嚟分類乜嘢為之高加索人種，乜嘢為之尼格羅人種（真正嘅黑鬼）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79a18e2f7a7d5a3a371859f42963f705fba6c7f8","tid":795476,"uid":166040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T07:59:35.000Z","msg":"玩total war 用過<br />\n算係非洲佬入面第二好用"},{"pid":"40ae0da6f6fb6aadee9e990925d4691b8a7b173c","tid":795476,"uid":199334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79a18e2f7a7d5a3a371859f42963f705fba6c7f8","tid":795476,"uid":166040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T07:59:35.000Z","msg":"玩total war 用過<br />\n算係非洲佬入面第二好用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T09:01:02.000Z","msg":"Attila <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a44608c05cd4b96a5ec066ec4014ae86f498bb8d","tid":795476,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79a18e2f7a7d5a3a371859f42963f705fba6c7f8","tid":795476,"uid":166040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T07:59:35.000Z","msg":"玩total war 用過<br />\n算係非洲佬入面第二好用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T10:31:59.000Z","msg":"我未買過 desert kingdoms dlc<br />\n但我睇kush呢個派系亦都唔惹少，埃及都經歷過由古實人-麥羅埃人掌權嘅黑鬼王朝，而古實人嘅領地都有起金字塔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係冇得用阿克蘇姆<br />\n<br />\n而attila其實只係得garamantes（柏柏爾人部落）同阿克蘇姆呢兩個非洲佬派系<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d0ecea23dab2d40b0151159be22808fbd06c093","tid":795476,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:08:33.000Z","msg":"咁剛果以西以南班黑人又有咩搞作"},{"pid":"48e12e3f57c8f16ef362c3b3f0e0604a68a89758","tid":795476,"uid":90457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0d0ecea23dab2d40b0151159be22808fbd06c093","tid":795476,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:08:33.000Z","msg":"咁剛果以西以南班黑人又有咩搞作"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:53:13.000Z","msg":"剛果以南嗰啲真係幾落後吓，雖然有鐵器貿易之類，但始終都係原始部落，未曾有建立大城市，班圖人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n西非都得意啲，大概喺現今馬里嘅位置，當地黑鬼都有黃金買賣，流通撒哈拉，而廷巴克圖曾經作為西非嘅伊斯蘭中心、馬里帝國貿易中心<br />\n後來喺馬里皇帝曼薩穆薩於14世紀帶同一車車嘅黃金、黑奴向麥加朝聖，途中佢發揚「有錢就大撚哂」嘅精神，郁吓就<span style=\"color: red;\">唔小心</span>跌黃金，導致當時北非同近東一帶嘅黃金貶值足足十幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過馬里只係對西非一帶嘅文化同伊斯蘭信仰帶嚟好大影響，即使「傑內清真寺」都唔係用磚建造，所以唔係好發達嘅國家但對於西非世界嚟講都算係咁"},{"pid":"ee3586e237aa3ca6b933b4ad07ff90cdd640eca4","tid":795476,"uid":35317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T15:28:51.000Z","msg":"有冇人研究過古埃及人到㡳係咩人種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3f62b90194a1906458595a5fa53329749ed4394","tid":795476,"uid":145357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T15:47:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/27/234734_246f5ca4eab9cf7aca7e22c55111758b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F27%2F234734_246f5ca4eab9cf7aca7e22c55111758b.png&h=3d024a5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有呢條友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01498ce4c1a2de322fb6db026651502cd232b7cd","tid":795476,"uid":106641